		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The flow chart illustrates the process which the Hong Kong Post Office [1] to select suitable artwork for its stamps.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
