		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The first stages [2] gathering ideas for possible themes. District councils, tourist associations and government departments are all [3] to send in suggestions to the Post Office. These are then forwarded to a special stamp advisory committee which [4] chooses between six and eight of the best ideas.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
